name: EmmaTheChef
0:
”Alexa, Open Emma The Chef”
”Alexa, Ask Emma The Chef to find some dinner options for me”
”Alexa, Tell Emma The Chef I want something for dinner”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: emma the chef
des:
EmmaTheChef is a virtual assistant chef that will provide you with breakfast, lunch, dinner, and snack recipes, with step by step instructions that will guide you in making a delicious meal. 
Want to make a healthy breakfast or maybe a dinner? EmmaTheChef can give you a list of suggestions at your choosing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
